Package wordle

Class HighscoreEntry

java.lang.Object
wordle.HighscoreEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<HighscoreEntry>
public class HighscoreEntry extends Object implements Comparable<HighscoreEntry>
Represents an entry in the highscore table for the Wordle game. Each entry consists of a level, score, and identification number.
